## Class Features

- **Fighting Style:** Defense (+1 AC while wearing armor)  
- **Second Wind:** Heal 1d10 + 7 (1/rest)  
- **Action Surge:** Take one extra action on your turn (1/rest)  
- **Extra Attack:** Attack twice when taking the Attack action  

### Battle Master Maneuvers
- **Trip Attack:** Knock foes prone  
- **Menacing Attack:** Frighten on hit (WIS save DC 14)  
- **Riposte:** Counterattack as reaction  
- **Superiority Dice:** 4d8 per short rest (save DC 14)  
- **Know Your Enemy:** Observe 1 min to gauge STR/CON

